  "detailed_description": "A challenging horror game versus an intelligent opponent that requires tactics and strategy to win.  Set in an atmospheric factory, can you defeat That Last Girl?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/1d6e50f76671b325c656b94ed4d668a3.poster.avif?t=1700682028\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/1d6e50f76671b325c656b94ed4d668a3.webm?t=1700682028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/1d6e50f76671b325c656b94ed4d668a3.mp4?t=1700682028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Intelligent monster, no set patrols, no endless random movement.  <strong>She will hunt you down.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/330a71de868f1460c0eb6d08ee6b24b9.poster.avif?t=1700682028\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/330a71de868f1460c0eb6d08ee6b24b9.webm?t=1700682028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/330a71de868f1460c0eb6d08ee6b24b9.mp4?t=1700682028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use light, sound and the factory layout itself to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/124c212af5d589ef645db7d9fe32d3f3.poster.avif?t=1700682028\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262910/extras/124c212af5